<h1>Change password</h1>
<p>On this page you can change your password to log in to ALVAO applications.</p>
  <p>If you are logged into Alvao with a Windows or Microsoft 365 account, you cannot change your password in the application. In that case, change your password directly in Windows or Microsoft 365.</p>
<p>Options:</p>
	<ul>
 <li><strong>Original password</strong>- enter your current password.</li>
 <li><strong>New Password</strong>- enter a new password.</li>
 <li><strong>Re-enter new password</strong>- re-enter your new password to check.</li>
	</ul>

</asp:Content>
